Not give in to weakness.

257
00:10:41,157 --> 00:10:43,274
- But it wasn't weakness that
made you break your word.

258
00:10:43,276 --> 00:10:44,909
It was love for your father.

259
00:10:44,911 --> 00:10:47,078
- Then aren't i an asshole?

260
00:10:47,080 --> 00:10:51,016
Because i ended up ruining
everything two weeks later.

261
00:10:52,919 --> 00:10:55,020
- Louis, i need to
talk to you for a minute.

262
00:10:55,022 --> 00:10:56,021
- About what?

263
00:10:56,023 --> 00:10:57,222
- Jack soloff is
calling for a vote

264
00:10:57,224 --> 00:11:01,126
To remove me as
managing partner today.

265
00:11:01,128 --> 00:11:02,394
- What?

266
00:11:02,396 --> 00:11:03,828
Why the hell would he do that

267
00:11:03,830 --> 00:11:05,096
After you offered to make him
name partner?

268
00:11:05,098 --> 00:11:06,965
- Because i didn't offer
to make him name partner.

269
00:11:06,967 --> 00:11:08,333
I told him to resign.

270
00:11:08,335 --> 00:11:09,367
- What happened to our plan?

271
00:11:09,369 --> 00:11:10,935
- It wasn't our plan, louis.

272
00:11:10,937 --> 00:11:12,871
It was your insane idea,

273
00:11:12,873 --> 00:11:14,072
And i was never going to do it.

274
00:11:14,074 --> 00:11:15,106
- Jessica...

275
00:11:15,108 --> 00:11:17,108
- No, you listen to me.

276
00:11:17,110 --> 00:11:18,810
The matter at hand is

277
00:11:18,812 --> 00:11:20,912
