281
00:11:25,852 --> 00:11:27,018
<i>In the first place.</i>

282
00:11:27,020 --> 00:11:29,521
You're gonna find out
what daniel has

283
00:11:29,522 --> 00:11:32,023
On that weaselly son of a bitch,
