284
00:11:32,025 --> 00:11:34,392
Because if i can't get
enough votes before then,

285
00:11:34,394 --> 00:11:37,729
The only way we win is to make
this whole thing go away.

286
00:11:37,731 --> 00:11:39,998
<i>[dramatic music]</i>

287
00:11:40,000 --> 00:11:41,266
- Cancel my day.

288
00:11:49,409 --> 00:11:49,841
.

