00:11:54,715 --> 00:11:56,281
- What i say i'm doing?

293
00:11:56,283 --> 00:11:58,316
- Father walker called me.

294
00:11:58,318 --> 00:11:59,718
He said you've been acting out.

295
00:11:59,720 --> 00:12:01,052
- Father walker's a priest.

296
00:12:01,054 --> 00:12:02,821
He thinks you're acting out
if you're chewing gum.

297
00:12:02,823 --> 00:12:04,473
- Well, i agree with him.

298
00:12:04,474 --> 00:12:06,124
- Yeah, and you're not at school
and all i do is get as.

299
00:12:06,126 --> 00:12:07,959
- I don't care
what you're getting.

300
00:12:07,961 --> 00:12:09,060
I found these in the trash.

301
00:12:09,062 --> 00:12:10,295
- So what.

302
00:12:10,297 --> 00:12:11,796
- So what?

303
00:12:11,798 --> 00:12:13,865
"the little prince,"
"james and the giant peach,"

