00:12:13,867 --> 00:12:15,333
Michael, you love these books.

305
00:12:15,335 --> 00:12:16,868
- Yeah, when i was a kid.

306
00:12:16,870 --> 00:12:18,136
- Those books were your
connection to your mother

307
00:12:18,138 --> 00:12:19,904
And father.

308
00:12:19,906 --> 00:12:23,975
- Yeah, well,
i don't want them anymore.

