never let me read it to you

314
00:12:37,124 --> 00:12:39,991
Because you said
it was so special.

315
00:12:39,993 --> 00:12:41,826
- Like i said,
i'm not a kid anymore.

316
00:12:41,828 --> 00:12:43,027
- Michael,
i'm worried about you.

317
00:12:43,029 --> 00:12:44,829
Father walker is worried.

318
00:12:44,831 --> 00:12:46,297
- I don't care what
father walker thinks,

319
00:12:46,299 --> 00:12:49,968
And i don't care about
these stupid books.

320
00:12:49,970 --> 00:12:52,170
- Well, i do care,

321
00:12:52,172 --> 00:12:54,506
And i think you'd better go talk
to father walker tomorrow

322
00:12:54,508 --> 00:12:57,108
Because you're not
getting all as.

323
00:12:57,110 --> 00:13:01,446
