331
00:13:19,032 --> 00:13:20,031
- Shut your mouth.

332
00:13:20,033 --> 00:13:22,050
You're not fit to
lick her boots.

333
00:13:22,051 --> 00:13:24,068
- Good, because that's
your job, louis, not mine.

334
00:13:24,070 --> 00:13:26,104
- Listen to me.

335
00:13:26,106 --> 00:13:27,505
Remember when i told you
i'd kill you

336
00:13:27,507 --> 00:13:30,074
